335
00:26:18,030 --> 00:26:19,170
Jerk!

336
00:26:19,420 --> 00:26:20,560
Then you can't die!

337
00:26:22,840 --> 00:26:24,420
Didn't you say that the outside world

338
00:26:24,420 --> 00:26:25,940
