483
00:38:29,180 --> 00:38:30,310
Not envious of the world.

484
00:38:31,890 --> 00:38:32,990
Only the cloud knows the feather.

485
00:38:48,120 --> 00:38:49,440
Why are you sneaking around

486
00:38:49,460 --> 00:38:50,270
